snippet.title: Good Morning Britain
snippet.description:
The Good Morning Britain YouTube channel delivers you the news that you’re waking up to in the morning.

From exclusive interviews with some of the biggest names in politics and showbiz to heartwarming human interest stories and unmissable watch again moments. 

Join Susanna Reid, Ben Shephard, Charlotte Hawkins, Piers Morgan, Kate Garraway and Sean Fletcher every weekday on ITV from 6am and visit www.itv.com/gmb for more!
